-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
P1               0       4       2        30           0         4         0           4         0       no
P2               1       3       1        30           7        10         6           9         6       no
P3               2       2       1        30           5         7         3           5         3       no
P4               3       1       1        30           4         5         1           2         1       no

